cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: QUIC Server Performance Data Under Controlled Network Conditions
abstract: ' This dataset contains results from experiments measuring QUIC server performance
  metrics under various controlled network conditions using IPv6. These measurements
  were conducted through multiple runs across three nodes with different configurations
  of network profiles and schedulers. Scripts provided the methodology for environment
  setup, traffic shaping, execution control, and result uploading to facilitate understanding.'
